race.comment: TRULY GALLANT (1) is going well, scoring by 3 lengths two runs back at this track before finishing fourth last time over this track and trip. Has a fine record here with two wins from six starts. Sure to go well. BOUSSAC (2) finished fifth two runs back at this track then improved last time out to score by a head after being prominent at the turn here. Looks well placed so expect another big run. BE MY BELLE (6) showed good speed and fought on for second here last time. Has been in sound form this prep with a win and two minor placings from four outings. Shapes as one to consider. NOBLE TOUCH (7) registered her first win last start here. Re-unites with Faithfull who was on board last start. Tougher assignment this time but is one of the main contenders.
